{"serial": "09064", "department_serial": 3, "code": "GS3711", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Data science and its applications on humanities and society", "ch": "資料科學與人文社會應用"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Shen, Chien-wen", "JHONG,JHEN-YAO"], "ch": ["沈建文", "鍾震耀"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "109"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "通識教育中心", "en": "General Education Center"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 29, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "資料科學與大數據分析已成為商業管理、人文社會科學等領域的熱門話題。此課程專為非IT特質學生而設計，讓他們有興趣運用數據分析方法分析商業數據。學生可以學習到的技術與方法包括資料分類技術、集群分析、關聯規則、文件探勘以及一些基於統計的方法。", "en": "Data science and big data analysis have become popular topics in fields such as business management and the humanities and social sciences. This course is designed specifically for students without an IT background, encouraging them to apply data analysis methods to analyze business data. The techniques and methods that students will learn include data classification techniques, cluster analysis, association rules, text mining, as well as some statistics-based methods."}, "outline": {"ch": "1.資料科學與人文社會應用課程介紹\n2.音樂大賞金曲獎--入圍與獲獎歌詞分析案例分享\n3.分析工具介紹與安裝\n4.從資料驅動談資料科學工作\n5.資料收集、資料整理、資料切割、資料統計、資料分析、資料詮釋(即說資料的故事)\n6.關聯規則(Association rules)介紹\n7.實作\na.距離與相似度\nb.集群分析(Clustering analysis)與顧客價值分析(R、F、M)介紹\nc.資料模型與預測\nd. 決策樹(Decision Tree)、KNN分類(Classification)介紹\ne.英文(English)文件探勘Text Mining介紹\nf.中文(Chinese)斷詞與中文文件探勘Text Mining介紹\n8.文字雲、文章重點\n9.文字的弦外之音—情緒篇(I)\n10.網路社群意見之情緒分析(Sentiment Analysis)介紹(非監督式)\n11.文字的弦外之音—情緒篇(II)\n12.網路社群意見之情緒分析(Sentiment Analysis)介紹(監督式)\n13.網路社群意見之主題模型(Topic Model)分析介紹(I)—白話文篇\n14.網路社群意見之主題模型(Topic Model)分析介紹(II)—文言文篇\n15.分組專案作業分享與檢討", "en": "1. Course Introduction to Data Science and its Applications in Humanities and Social Sciences\n2. Music Awards and Golden Melody Awards – Case Study on Lyric Analysis of Nominations and Winners\n3. Introduction and Installation of Analytical Tools\n4. Data-Driven Discussion on Data Science Work\n5/ Data Collection, Data Organization, Data Segmentation, Data Statistics, Data Analysis, Data Interpretation (i.e., Telling the Story of Data)\n6. Introduction to Association Rules\n7. Practical Applications\na. Distance and Similarity\nb. Introduction to Clustering Analysis and Customer Value Analysis (RFM)\nc. Data Modeling and Prediction\nd. Introduction to Decision Trees and KNN Classification\ne. Introduction to Text Mining of English Documents\nf. Introduction to Chinese Word Segmentation and Text Mining of Chinese Documents\n8. Word Clouds and Key Points of Articles\n9. The Unspoken Meaning of Text – Emotions (Part I)\n10. Introduction to Sentiment Analysis of Online Social Community Opinions (Unsupervised)\n11. The Unspoken Meaning of Text – Emotions (Part II)\n12. Introduction to Sentiment Analysis of Online Social Community Opinions (Supervised)\n13. Introduction to Topic Modeling Analysis of Online Social Community Opinions (Part I) – Vernacular Chinese\n14. Introduction to Topic Modeling Analysis of Online Social Community Opinions (Part II) – Classical Chinese\n15. Group Project Presentation and Review"}, "textbook": {"ch": "自編教材", "en": "Self-compiled teaching materials"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100", "en": "100"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n\n\n其他", "en": ["Lecture", "", "", "", "Others"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "期中考(15％)、期末考(15％)、課堂出席與互動(20％)、人社關懷互助(10％)、期末專案(30％)、練習回報(10％)", "en": "Midterm Exam (15％), Final Exam (15％), Class Attendance and Participation (20％), Social Care and Support (10％), Final Project (30％), Practice Reports (10％)."}, "officeHour": {"ch": "17:00-18:00 on Monday @ I1-834-1", "en": "17:00-18:00 on Monday @ I1-834-1"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscrip